entering the centre.} ({In the endgame that arises after}10. c5 d6 11. cxd6 Rd8 
12. e4 Qxd1 13. Rxd1 Rxd6 14. Rxd6 exd6 {the active piece play fully compensates 
for the weak d6-pawn, as was proven in a dozen games.} ) d6 ({The timid}10... Nxd5 
11. cxd5 Ne5 {, as was seen in some games before runs into} 12. d6 $146 $1 exd6 
13. Bf4 g5 {This is the only adequate way of liberating the poor Bc8, but it makes 
