16. h3 Nf6 17. g4 Qg6 18. f4 $36 ) 16. Qxd5 Qxe2 17. Nd4 Qh5 18. Rae1 $36 {White's 
initiative is more important than the the pawn.} ) 11. Nf4 $1 {This concrete approach 
